snippet.title: Mists of Pandaria Classic Announce Trailer | World of Warcraft Classic
snippet.description:
Follow a lone monk during his training regimen, as he relives fond memories of his past and grapples with dark visions of the future in a new trailer produced in collaboration with Hurricane.  

Mists of Pandaria is coming to WoW: Classic in 2025. 

► Visit Hurricane’s channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/Hurricane046  
► Latest WoW news: http://worldofwarcraft.com/news 
► Subscribe to WoW: http://blizz.ly/WoWYTSub
► Visit WoW on Battle.net: https://shop.battle.net/family/world-of-warcraft
